1
00:00:04,554 --> 00:00:09,024
Krishna knows no rules, constraints.

2
00:00:09,024 --> 00:00:13,734
It’s the ultimate, absolute, 
free flow of love from the heart.

3
00:00:14,274 --> 00:00:17,645
[You Can’t Handle the Truth!]

4
00:00:18,422 --> 00:00:21,761
So he said, “Autocrat, despot and liar.”

5
00:00:21,761 --> 00:00:26,250
Autocrat means 
exists for Himself and by Himself.

6
00:00:26,250 --> 00:00:30,960
Ultimately, He is everything. 
Right? Even we are told,

7
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:34,148
mamaivāṁśo jīva-loke, jīva-bhūtaḥ sanātanaḥ
[Bg: 15.7]

8
00:00:34,148 --> 00:00:38,076
That jiva-souls are the parts 
and parcels of Krishna.

9
00:00:38,076 --> 00:00:45,860
So when it comes to things, considerations,
like, whether or not, when Krishna ...

10
00:00:45,860 --> 00:00:50,950
Krishna has violated any moral code

11
00:00:50,950 --> 00:00:58,110
by His behaviour 
with the Braja-gopis, that ...

12
00:01:00,870 --> 00:01:03,675
It’s mentioned, 
“They all bel.ong to Him anyway.”

13
00:01:03,675 --> 00:01:09,960
So it’s not only that everything belongs 
to Krishna, we also belong to Krishna.

14
00:01:09,960 --> 00:01:14,507
So there’s no ... Really, ultimately, 
even when He is playing, they are all ...

15
00:01:14,507 --> 00:01:21,604
If you could say, an aggressor 
or transgressing some laws,

16
00:01:21,604 --> 00:01:25,106
or ‘stealing’ the property of others—

17
00:01:25,106 --> 00:01:26,741
really, it’s all the play.

18
00:01:26,741 --> 00:01:29,836
Because everything belongs to Him.

19
00:01:29,836 --> 00:01:34,841
So, autocrat followed by despot,

20
00:01:34,841 --> 00:01:38,856
an even more alarming sounding word 
Srila Guru Maharaj used

21
00:01:38,856 --> 00:01:45,641
because he is saying, “Despot means 
there should be no check on His autocracy.”

22
00:01:45,641 --> 00:01:51,989
If we tried to check the movements 
of Divinity, then we become losers.

23
00:01:52,456 --> 00:01:56,351
So therefore He needs to be 
in the position of a despot.

24
00:01:56,351 --> 00:02:02,207
He is the absolute good, everything 
He does is absolutely good for everyone.

25
00:02:02,207 --> 00:02:08,720
So there should be no check 
or restriction upon Him. So, despot.

26
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:17,354
But then Guru Maharaj told, “Liar”—
this was little more difficult to digest.

27
00:02:17,354 --> 00:02:25,253
And, we may point out, it’s not 
a conventional way of praising the Lord ...

28
00:02:25,253 --> 00:02:32,093
“My dear Lord, You are an autocrat, 
despot and liar ...

29
00:02:32,093 --> 00:02:36,653
And I am offering myself 
to You in service.”

30
00:02:36,653 --> 00:02:42,463
So when we have heard, “All right, we get it. 
Autocrat—Reality exists for Itself, by Itself.

31
00:02:42,463 --> 00:02:46,563
Despot—there should be no check on
because He is the absolute good.

32
00:02:46,563 --> 00:02:49,943
Everything He does is absolutely good 
for everyone ...”

33
00:02:49,943 --> 00:02:53,323
But one devotee said, “But liar?”

34
00:02:53,323 --> 00:02:58,742
And Guru Maharaj said, “Yes! Because 
you are not ready to hear the truth.”

35
00:02:58,742 --> 00:03:05,704
Like in a movie, where the man goes, 
“You can’t handle the truth!”

36
00:03:05,704 --> 00:03:09,844
So it’s something like that. 
We can’t handle the truth.

37
00:03:11,194 --> 00:03:12,844
What is part of that truth?

38
00:03:12,844 --> 00:03:22,593
That the Ultimate Reality, Krishna, 
He is appearing humanlike,

39
00:03:22,593 --> 00:03:27,882
in humanlike dimensions, proportions, 
tendencies, form.

40
00:03:28,082 --> 00:03:31,894
People think, “Well, I am comfortable 
with the Infinite—it’s grater than the greatest,

41
00:03:31,894 --> 00:03:36,144
all-accommodating, smaller 
than the smallest, all-permeating.”

42
00:03:36,344 --> 00:03:43,414
But that the central conception 
of the Infinite would be humanlike?

43
00:03:45,143 --> 00:03:49,317
And what would be 
the most superior position?

44
00:03:49,317 --> 00:03:52,317
As one is all-accommodating, 
[another is] all-permeating,

45
00:03:52,317 --> 00:03:54,783
what is the central conception 
of the Infinite?

46
00:03:54,783 --> 00:04:00,444
All-attractive. Reality the Beautiful.

47
00:04:00,503 --> 00:04:06,526
That the Ultimate Reality is beauty, 
love, charm and sweetness.

